---
title: Indonesian Chicken Fried Rice with Crunchy Chili Cashews
description: A take-out classic, fried rice is a favourite of many. This dish is packed with fresh flavours and wholesome brown rice. Bonus, it's ready in no time, so you'll be eating before you know it.
